item.title: OSCE Exam Tips
item.description: Just finished my OSCE Exam. And i wanted to contribute a quick blog post regarding the exam/course since i used alot of these myself to prepare. Ill start by laying out some key things i think that helped me pass and eleborate on each with some more details. Keep in mind this is meant to be very to the point and will not detail my exam experience such as time i took etc.
